The paper focuses on pattern recognition, specifically text recognition, using deep convolutional neural networks. This falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. The paper also introduces new concepts and techniques for improving the performance of deep networks, which could be relevant to machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories.
